paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

DROP TABLE  sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_01;
CREATE TABLE  sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_01 stored as orc as

select
c.*
from
(select
b.*,
row_number () over(partition by mes, id_celda order by fl_estado, fecha_de_estado desc) rnk
from
(select
a.*,
case when estado = 'Comercial' then 1
     when estado = 'PruebasLTE' then 2
     when estado = 'Swap' then 3
     when estado = 'Integrado' then 4
     when estado = 'Liberado' then 5
     when estado = "Planificado" then 6
     when estado = 'Des-definido' then 7
     when estado = 'Baja' then 8
     else 9
     end fl_estado
from
(select
substring(fecha, 1,6) as mes,
id_celda,
sector,
estado,
sitio,
latitud,
longitud,
radio_de_cobertura,
altura,
azimuth,
apertura_horizontal,
banda_mhz,
tipo_inst_sitio,
localidad,
provincia,
cabecera,
region,
subregion,
tecnologia,
fecha_de_estado
from tableros.listado_celdas_sectores
where fecha =date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMMdd') ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------> ultimo dia mes 
and id_celda is not null) a) b) c
where rnk = 1;


DROP TABLE  sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_02;
CREATE TABLE  sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_02 stored as orc as

select
mes,
sitio,
sum (case when tecnologia='2G' then 1 else 0 end) fl_2G,
sum (case when tecnologia='3G' then 1 else 0 end) fl_3G,
sum (case when tecnologia='4G' then 1 else 0 end) fl_4G,
sum (case when tecnologia='NULO' then 1 else 0 end) fl_nulo
from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_01
group by mes,sitio
;

DROP TABLE  sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_03;
CREATE TABLE  sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_03 stored as orc as
select
a.mes,
a.sitio,
(case when a.sitio = 'indefinido' then '8. indefinido'
when fl_2g>0 and fl_3g>0 and Fl_4g>0 then '1.Todos'
when fl_2g=0 and fl_3g>0 and Fl_4G>0 then '2.3G y 4G'
when fl_2g=0 and fl_3g=0 and Fl_4G>0 then '4.Solo 4G'
when fl_2g>0 and fl_3g=0 and Fl_4G=0 then '7.Solo 2G'
when fl_2g=0 and fl_3g>0 and Fl_4G=0 then '6.Solo 3G'
when fl_2g>0 and fl_3g=0 and Fl_4G>0 then '3.2G y 4G'
when fl_2g>0 and fl_3g>0 and Fl_4G=0 then '5.2G y 3G'
else 'ver' end) fl_sitio,
case when (b.sitio is null and d.sitio is null) then 0 else 1 end as fl_sitio_banda_4,
case when c.sitio is null then 0 else 1 end as fl_sitio_banda_2,
case when e.sitio is null then 0 else 1 end as fl_sitio_banda_7,
case when f.sitio is null then 0 else 1 end as fl_sitio_banda_28,
case when g.sitio is null then 0 else 1 end as fl_sitio_banda_5,
case when h.sitio is null then 0 else 1 end as fl_sitio_banda_2_5
from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_02 a
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_01 where banda_mhz ='1700/2100' group by mes,sitio)b  on a.sitio=b.sitio and a.mes=b.mes
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_01 where banda_mhz ='1900' group by mes,sitio)c  on a.sitio=c.sitio and a.mes=c.mes
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_01 where banda_mhz ='2100' group by mes,sitio)d  on a.sitio=d.sitio and a.mes=d.mes
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_01 where banda_mhz ='2600' group by mes,sitio)e  on a.sitio=e.sitio and a.mes=e.mes
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_01 where banda_mhz ='700' group by mes,sitio)f  on a.sitio=f.sitio and a.mes=f.mes
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_01 where banda_mhz ='850' group by mes,sitio)g  on a.sitio=g.sitio and a.mes=g.mes
left join (select mes, sitio, count(sitio) as Q from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_01 where banda_mhz ='850/1900' group by mes,sitio)h  on a.sitio=h.sitio and a.mes=h.mes
;

DROP TABLE  sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_10;
CREATE TABLE  sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_10 stored as orc as
select x.*,
(x.porc_banda_2_5 + x.porc_banda_2 + x.porc_banda_5) as porc_bandas_3g,
(x.porc_banda_4 + x.porc_banda_7 + x.porc_banda_28) as porc_bandas_4g,
case when (x.porc_banda_2_5 + x.porc_banda_2 + x.porc_banda_5)>(x.porc_banda_4 + x.porc_banda_7 + x.porc_banda_28) then 1 else 0 end as fl_mayoritario_bandas_3g
from (
select 
a.mes,
a.ani,
nvl(b.mb,0) as banda_28,
nvl(c.mb,0) as banda_2_5,
nvl(d.mb,0) as banda_4,
nvl(e.mb,0) as banda_2,
nvl(f.mb,0) as banda_5,
nvl(g.mb,0) as banda_7,
nvl(h.mb,0) as total,
nvl(b.mb / h.mb,0) porc_banda_28,
nvl(c.mb / h.mb,0) porc_banda_2_5,
nvl(d.mb / h.mb,0) porc_banda_4,
nvl(e.mb / h.mb,0) porc_banda_2,
nvl(f.mb / h.mb,0) porc_banda_5,
nvl(g.mb / h.mb,0) porc_banda_7,
row_number ()  over (partition by a.ani order by a.ani) orden
from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_08 a
left join (select  mes , ani, mb from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_08 where banda_ok='28')b on a.ani=b.ani and a.mes=b.mes
left join (select  mes, ani, mb from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_08 where banda_ok='2-5')c on a.ani=c.ani and a.mes=c.mes
left join (select  mes, ani, mb from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_08 where banda_ok='4')d on a.ani=d.ani and a.mes=d.mes
left join (select  mes, ani, mb from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_08 where banda_ok='2')e on a.ani=e.ani and a.mes=e.mes
left join (select  mes, ani, mb from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_08 where banda_ok='5')f on a.ani=f.ani and a.mes=f.mes
left join (select  mes, ani, mb from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_08 where banda_ok='7')g on a.ani=g.ani and a.mes=g.mes
left join (select  mes, ani, sum(mb) as mb from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_08 where banda_ok<>'N/A' group by mes, ani)h on a.ani=h.ani and a.mes=h.mes
)x where x.orden=1
;
